social_posts.post_text: Spring Themed Mugs 🌷

These past couple of years have been difficult in many ways, cherished pets passing and most recently losing my mom in February. Grief is something that we all will experience at some point in our lives, multiple losses around the same time can be extra difficult but you just have to trudge through it, there are no short cuts. The pain is a result of all the love we have in our hearts. But now is time for some joyful news. This is Shiloh, he is 8 weeks old German Shepard. Isn’t he the cutest puppy??? So precious, he and Nina now have their own page @nina_and_shiloh_von_artur if you want to see more pictures as they come. Andover Pottery is slowly getting back into the swing of things. I hope to post more pottery pictures and also share some of our garden adventures ❤️. #andoverpottery
